    "translatedContent": "   - Docker इमेजेज? हट गईं 🗑️"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "gb9RnoW4YbyiVe8xkUDDfnWDCf2sb9jFDYWpm419ySo=",
    "originContent": "   - Language runtimes? Obliterated 💥",
    "translatedContent": "   - लैंग्वेज रनटाइम्स? नष्ट 💥"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "u8ad+VsFP7rZv3BSnMufzyq8p6NU1KTVdCctG56RqwE=",
    "originContent": "   - Package managers? Annihilated 💣",
    "translatedContent": "   - पैकेज मैनेजर? विनष्ट 💣"
  },
